-08T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"樓主等緊你既少女時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一個故都好好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"等多兩個月，呢兩個月會連載呢個校園小品同埋另一個長篇故《全力爆籃》，十月初（深知最快九月尾）一定有少女時代！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！"},{"pid":"3957ba335e6dd4d7e768d9b9f475255180b1e6ab","tid":766455,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主等緊你既少女時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一個故都好好睇</blockquote>等多兩個月，呢兩個月會連載呢個校園小品同埋另一個長篇故《全力爆籃》，十月初（<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甚至</strong></span></span>最快九月尾）一定有少女時代！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9412b809fdfe873e677e2b7f5838d103c1e00b3d","tid":766455,"uid":161406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【第五種】有借冇還</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/214952_308ec23709872bfbfd2a2b975b121008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F214952_308ec23709872bfbfd2a2b975b121008.jpg&h=3c64a3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「行了...我知道了...很快就還！」<br />\n<br />\n中學六年，聽見這句話的次數可真是不勝枚舉。<br />\n<br />\n不單是金錢上，更有可能是文具、筆記、書等等等等......<br />\n<br />\n中學生涯中總會遇上一個「有借冇還」的同學，一旦你借了東西給他，他總有百般理由來拒絕你的詢問。<br />\n<br />\n「帶不夠錢...能先幫我結帳嗎...？」午膳時間，同學有難，我當然義不容辭的先給他付錢。<br />\n<br />\n天真的我認為一個人借了別人的東西，總會主動歸還的。怎料借錢的人卻往往把此事拋諸腦後，見面時若無其事，開口問他又是尷尬，讓人進退兩難。<br />\n<br />\n終於我鼓起勇氣問他還錢一事，他卻竟然笑言錢包不在身；<br />\n<br />\n第二次錢包在身時，他竟主動拿出錢包遞給我，滿心歡喜的我翻開錢包，裡面卻竟空空如也......<br />\n<br />\n第三次、第四次&hellip;...<br />\n<br />\n終於，你也懶得問他還錢一事；終於...他自此之後也再沒提及過此事。<br />\n<br />\n而比起「借錢而不還」，「借文具而不見」就顯得更為普遍。<br />\n<br />\n依舊是同學一場，作文、考試前突然發現原子筆沒墨水、忘記帶塗改帶......<br />\n<br />\n我有非正式統計過，借出去的文具，十件有八件都如進入百慕達三角，自此消失不見，再也回不來自己手上。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這些大部分相比起日後踏入社會所經歷的「欠」和「還」，也就顯得十分細微。而我們現在所經歷的，或許已經成為了中學的傳統......<br />\n<br />\n每個人，都會經歷一段「有借冇還」的歷史......<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「得啦...好快還！」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8943f5bfd49a9d4bd7365e274e1237ff14b5963a","tid":766455,"uid":107555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"live"},{"pid":"f2be4feecc5428b72ec659b47856b86458aa04d3","tid":766455,"uid":161406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8943f5bfd49a9d4bd7365e274e1237ff14b5963a","tid":766455,"uid":107555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"live"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4743067b55af53371d84cd192e5dadb1f0693b","tid":766455,"uid":148245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c87677b4fca380409f2752ff4db3e9d6d373e0d5","tid":766455,"uid":161406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb4743067b55af53371d84cd192e5dadb1f0693b","tid":766455,"uid":148245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"多謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2b1a9b9b54593013ebdead2937fbdaf57ae4b1","tid":766455,"uid":160066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"咁爭落嘅文幾時還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gi